Package presentation

Class PalettePresentation

java.lang.Object
presentation.PalettePresentation
public class PalettePresentation
extends java.lang.Object
PalettePresentation is intended to be used as a part of a BlockAreaCanvas. PalettePresentation handles activities concerning the palette.
Version:
4.0
Author:
Andreas Awouters Thomas Van Erum Dirk Vanbeveren Geert Wesemael
